                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed space-y-2 mt-4">
                    <li>Card and digital payment processing via integrated processor connections.</li>
                    <li>Fund settlement via our sponsoring bank(s) and acquiring partners.</li>
                    <li>Reporting dashboards and reconciliation tools.</li>
                    <li>Secure data storage via tokenization and PCI DSS Level 1-compliant infrastructure.</li>
                    <li>Optional value-add services such as recurring billing, fraud prevention tools, and ACH payment processing.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 mb-4 border-b pb-2 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800">2. Fees and Pricing</h2>
